main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Chicago, Illinois on August 25, 1955, involving three cylindrical objects approximately six feet in length, described as blue with white exhaust, circling the area for ten minutes.
interesting points: The sighting involved three cylindrical objects with white exhaust circling Chicago for ten minutes.
The observer was apparently intoxicated at the time of the sighting, according to the report.
The sighting was reported by long distance telephone.
No photographs were included in the report.
The observer's description was deemed frequently vague.
sighted object: three cylindrical objects with white exhaust
